  "class.sensoryabyss.the_blinded.description": "Having lost your sight, you now perceive the world through sound. Mark your prey and claim their bounties.",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_deafened": "The Deafened",
  "class.sensoryabyss.the_deafened.description": "Deaf to the world's sounds, you feel every tremor in the earth. Your journey grants seismic awareness.",
